   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Diodoros and partners, praktors of the crown-tax of the village of Theogonis, to Aion son of Apynchis, greeting. We have received from you for crown-tax of the 22nd (?) year, for the account of Hathyr 4 drachmas, Tybi 4 drachmas, Mecheir 16 obols, Pharmouthi 12 obols, Payni 16 obols, Mesore 16 obols, Phaophi 12 obols.</ab>
